26#ifndef __GF100_GR_H__
27#define __GF100_GR_H__
28#define gf100_gr(p) container_of((p), struct gf100_gr, base)
29#include "priv.h"
30
31#include <core/gpuobj.h>
32#include <subdev/ltc.h>
33#include <subdev/mmu.h>
34
35#define GPC_MAX 32
36#define TPC_MAX (GPC_MAX * 8)
37
38#define ROP_BCAST(r) (0x408800 + (r))
39#define ROP_UNIT(u, r) (0x410000 + (u) * 0x400 + (r))
40#define GPC_BCAST(r) (0x418000 + (r))
41#define GPC_UNIT(t, r) (0x500000 + (t) * 0x8000 + (r))
42#define PPC_UNIT(t, m, r) (0x503000 + (t) * 0x8000 + (m) * 0x200 + (r))
43#define TPC_UNIT(t, m, r) (0x504000 + (t) * 0x8000 + (m) * 0x800 + (r))
44
45struct gf100_gr_data {
46 u32 size;
47 u32 align;
48 u32 access;
49};
50
51struct gf100_gr_mmio {
52 u32 addr;
53 u32 data;
54 u32 shift;
55 int buffer;
56};
57
58struct gf100_gr_fuc {
59 u32 *data;
60 u32 size;
61};
62
63struct gf100_gr_zbc_color {
64 u32 format;
65 u32 ds[4];
66 u32 l2[4];
67};
68
69struct gf100_gr_zbc_depth {
70 u32 format;
71 u32 ds;
72 u32 l2;
73};
74
75struct gf100_gr {
76 const struct gf100_gr_func *func;
77 struct nvkm_gr base;
78
79 struct gf100_gr_fuc fuc409c;
80 struct gf100_gr_fuc fuc409d;
81 struct gf100_gr_fuc fuc41ac;
82 struct gf100_gr_fuc fuc41ad;
83 bool firmware;
84
85 /*
86 * Used if the register packs are loaded from NVIDIA fw instead of
87 * using hardcoded arrays.
88 */
89 struct gf100_gr_pack *fuc_sw_nonctx;
90 struct gf100_gr_pack *fuc_sw_ctx;
91 struct gf100_gr_pack *fuc_bundle;
92 struct gf100_gr_pack *fuc_method;
93
94 struct gf100_gr_zbc_color zbc_color[NVKM_LTC_MAX_ZBC_CNT];
95 struct gf100_gr_zbc_depth zbc_depth[NVKM_LTC_MAX_ZBC_CNT];
96
97 u8 rop_nr;
98 u8 gpc_nr;
99 u8 tpc_nr[GPC_MAX];
100 u8 tpc_total;
101 u8 ppc_nr[GPC_MAX];
102 u8 ppc_mask[GPC_MAX];
103 u8 ppc_tpc_nr[GPC_MAX][4];
104
105 struct nvkm_memory *unk4188b4;
106 struct nvkm_memory *unk4188b8;
107
108 struct gf100_gr_data mmio_data[4];
109 struct gf100_gr_mmio mmio_list[4096/8];
110 u32 size;
111 u32 *data;
112
113 u8 magic_not_rop_nr;
114};
115
116int gf100_gr_ctor(const struct gf100_gr_func *, struct nvkm_device *,
117 int, struct gf100_gr *);
118int gf100_gr_new_(const struct gf100_gr_func *, struct nvkm_device *,
119 int, struct nvkm_gr **);
120void *gf100_gr_dtor(struct nvkm_gr *);
121
122struct gf100_gr_func {
123 void (*dtor)(struct gf100_gr *);
124 int (*init)(struct gf100_gr *);
125 void (*init_gpc_mmu)(struct gf100_gr *);
126 void (*set_hww_esr_report_mask)(struct gf100_gr *);
127 const struct gf100_gr_pack *mmio;
128 struct {
129 struct gf100_gr_ucode *ucode;
130 } fecs;
131 struct {
132 struct gf100_gr_ucode *ucode;
133 } gpccs;
134 int ppc_nr;
135 const struct gf100_grctx_func *grctx;
136 struct nvkm_sclass sclass[];
137};

183struct gf100_gr_pack {

185 u32 type;
186};

188#define pack_for_each_init(init, pack, head) \
189 for (pack = head; pack && pack->init; pack++) \
190 for (init = pack->init; init && init->count; init++)
